FundManager V2 agent rules

Always treat repo docs as source of truth.

Core constraints:
- Keep Android local-first unless docs explicitly say otherwise.
- Do not replace Room with another database.
- Do not change money fields to Double or Float.
- Keep all currency math in Long / bigint style integers.
- Do not assume one device equals one user.
- Preserve existing soft-delete behavior unless a migration plan is documented.
- Keep changes small and additive by default.
- Inspect relevant files before editing.
- Summarize risks and files to change before making code edits.
- Run the most relevant tests after changes when possible.
- Prefer updating docs when design or policy changes.

Reference docs:
